snippet.textDisplay: Stigma is an emotional issue and should not be associated with science fact. If it comes from a country any country it should be recognized as such because of the genetic diversity or isolation within the population so we can figure out a way to approach the varient , if it destroys the citizens of that country or has no effect due to genetic variability or environmental factors or both
